Import Data Browser-Days to Transaction - Users

DA <-  read_excel("~/Desktop/Job related/Surefoot/Surefoot 2/Surefoot- GA/Analysis - 2/test and control dates/Returning Users + Browser/browser+daystotxn.xlsx", sheet = 2)

Data wrangling

DA_01 <- DA 
 names(DA)
##  [1] "Browser"                   "Days to Transaction"      
##  [3] "Date Range"                "Segment"                  
##  [5] "Users"                     "New Users"                
##  [7] "Sessions"                  "Bounce Rate"              
##  [9] "Pages / Session"           "Avg. Session Duration"    
## [11] "Ecommerce Conversion Rate" "Transactions"             
## [13] "Revenue"
colnames(DA_01)[colnames(DA_01)=="Days to Transaction"] <- "Days_to_Transaction"  
colnames(DA_01)[colnames(DA_01)=="Date Range"] <- "Date_Range" 
colnames(DA_01)[colnames(DA_01)=="Bounce Rate"] <- "Bounce_Rate"
colnames(DA_01)[colnames(DA_01)=="Pages / Session"] <- "Page_Sesion"
colnames(DA_01)[colnames(DA_01)=="Avg. Session Duration"] <- "Avg_Session_Duration"
colnames(DA_01)[colnames(DA_01)=="Ecommerce Conversion Rate"] <- "E_Conversion_Rate"
 
  

DA_02 <- DA_01 %>% filter(!is.na(Browser))

DA_03 <- DA_02 %>% mutate(test_categ = ifelse(Date_Range == "Oct 18, 2019 - Oct 31, 2019", "test-Oct 18,2019 - Oct 31,2019", "control-Oct 4,2019 - Oct 17,2019"))

DT_m <- DA_03 %>% filter(Date_Range == "Oct 18, 2019 - Oct 31, 2019")

Visualization Days to Txn- Browser Users

DA_20 <- DA_03 %>% select( Browser, Days_to_Transaction, Revenue, test_categ)
 
  
DA_24 <- DA_20 %>% select(Browser, Days_to_Transaction, Revenue, test_categ) %>% group_by(Browser, Days_to_Transaction, test_categ) %>% mutate(TotR = sum(Revenue)) %>% select(Browser, Days_to_Transaction, TotR,  test_categ)
DA_25 <- unique(DA_24) 
 

DA_25$Days_to_Transaction<- as.factor(DA_25$Days_to_Transaction) 
DA_25 %>% filter(TotR > 0) %>% 
ggplot(aes(reorder(x=Browser, TotR), y=TotR, fill=Days_to_Transaction)) + 
  geom_bar(stat="identity", position = "dodge")  + theme(plot.title = element_text(size =10),axis.text.x = element_text(size =7,angle = 65, hjust = 1) ) + ggtitle("Browser by Days to Transaction  for Returned Users") +xlab("Browser") + ylab("Total Revenue") +  scale_fill_manual(values=c("#F8766D", "#39B600",  "#9590FF", "#FF62BC", "#D89000", "#00C1A3", "#A3A500", "#EA8331", "#00BFCD", "#00B4F0", "#00BFC4" )) + guides(colour = guide_legend(override.aes = list(size=3, alpha = 1))) + scale_shape_manual(values=c(3:9)) + facet_wrap(~test_categ)

Import Data Browser-Device - Users

DA <-  read_excel("~/Desktop/Job related/Surefoot/Surefoot 2/Surefoot- GA/Analysis - 2/test and control dates/Returning Users + Browser/browser+device.xlsx", sheet = 2)

Data wrangling

DA_01 <- DA 
 names(DA)
##  [1] "Browser"                   "Device Category"          
##  [3] "Date Range"                "Segment"                  
##  [5] "Users"                     "New Users"                
##  [7] "Sessions"                  "Bounce Rate"              
##  [9] "Pages / Session"           "Avg. Session Duration"    
## [11] "Ecommerce Conversion Rate" "Transactions"             
## [13] "Revenue"
colnames(DA_01)[colnames(DA_01)=="New Users"] <- "New_Users"  
colnames(DA_01)[colnames(DA_01)=="Date Range"] <- "Date_Range" 
colnames(DA_01)[colnames(DA_01)=="Bounce Rate"] <- "Bounce_Rate"
colnames(DA_01)[colnames(DA_01)=="Pages / Session"] <- "Page_Sesion"
colnames(DA_01)[colnames(DA_01)=="Avg. Session Duration"] <- "Avg_Session_Duration"
colnames(DA_01)[colnames(DA_01)=="Ecommerce Conversion Rate"] <- "E_Conversion_Rate"
colnames(DA_01)[colnames(DA_01)=="Device Category"] <- "Device"
 
  

DA_02 <- DA_01 %>% filter(!is.na(Browser))

DA_03_01 <- DA_02 %>% mutate(test_categ = ifelse(Date_Range == "Oct 18, 2019 - Oct 31, 2019", "test-Oct 18,2019 - Oct 31,2019", "control-Oct 4,2019 - Oct 17,2019"))
DA_03 <- DA_03_01 %>% filter(Device != "tablet")

DD_m <- DA_03 %>% filter(Date_Range == "Oct 18, 2019 - Oct 31, 2019")

Visualization Device - Browser Users

DA_20 <- DA_03 %>% select( Browser, Device, Revenue, test_categ)
 
  
DA_24 <- DA_20 %>% select(Browser, Device, Revenue, test_categ) %>% group_by(Browser, Device, test_categ) %>% mutate(TotR = sum(Revenue)) %>% select(Browser, Device, TotR,  test_categ)

DA_25$Device<- as.factor(DA_25$Device)

ggplot(aes(reorder(x=Browser, TotR), y=TotR, fill=Device)) + 
  geom_bar(stat="identity", position = "dodge")  + theme(plot.title = element_text(size =10),axis.text.x = element_text(size =7,angle = 65, hjust = 1) ) + ggtitle("Browser by Device for Returning Users") +xlab("Browser") + ylab("Total Revenue") +  scale_fill_manual(values=c("#F8766D", "#39B600",  "#9590FF", "#FF62BC", "#D89000", "#00C1A3", "#A3A500", "#EA8331", "#00BFCD", "#00B4F0", "#00BFC4" )) + guides(colour = guide_legend(override.aes = list(size=3, alpha = 1))) + scale_shape_manual(values=c(3:9)) + facet_wrap(~test_categ)
